page.title: 20Wetwang,Transport
page.content: In Wetwang there is not very much traffic but on the Main Street there is quite alot.There are usually quite alot of heavy lorries going through Main Street during the day and there are alot of cars too. We have a few fast drivers in Wetwang and we have motorbikes as well but not many.Lots of people ride bikes round Wetwang and some ride them to work. We get quite alot of tractors (and in harvest quite a few combines) because we have alot of farms around Wetwang. There is only one bus service and that goes to Driffield.It only goes once a day and if you miss it that's it.You really need a car if you live here and if you haven't got one you're stuck!
